title: Chiara Salome
abstract:
Chiara Salome is a Berlin based DJ presenting an ambient techno set. Carefully selected tracks from genres like techno, spiritual music, drone, dark ambient, 90's IDM and even symphonic music are
entangled into a marvellous tapestry of sound. She loves to play with music which is rich of textures, glowering bases and eatherical atmospheres providing the listener a meditative and trippy experience with surprising turns.
